  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "(AUTONOMOUS)"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "NBKRIST gave me confidence, skills, and the right environment to grow into a future engineer."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "Supportive environment with good faculty and infrastructure. Great opportunities for learning and activities."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "The peaceful campus and supportive faculty make learning enjoyable every day."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "Every semester brought new learning opportunities and confidence."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "NBKRIST gave me confidence and direction."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "My college years were instrumental in shaping my professional path. The faculty's guidance combined with exposure to industry-oriented projects and cultural activities, helped me build a well-rounded skill set.This holistic development has been key to my growth in the software industry.."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "I am proud to be part of NBKRIST."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "Every semester brought new learning opportunities and confidence."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "NBKRIST laid the foundation for my successful software career."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "My journey from classroom to corporate began at NBKRIST."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "I owe much of my professional success to NBKRIST."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "We saw remarkable growth in our child after joining NBKRIST."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "My college years were instrumental in shaping my professional path. The faculty's guidance combined with exposure to industry-oriented projects and cultural activities, helped me build a well-rounded skill set.This holistic development has been key to my growth in the software industry.."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "A knowledge hub with rich collections of books, journals, e-resources and peaceful study spaces supporting academic excellence. Well equipped library with more than 44,197 books and 267 periodicals."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "Dedicated Career Development and Placement Cell providing placement support, industry internships, skill training and career guidance with top recruiters visiting campus."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "Modern infrastructure, digital classrooms, laboratories, Wi-Fi campus and green surroundings designed for quality learning and continuous growth."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "Sports, clubs, cultural events, NSS, NCC and leadership opportunities that shape confident all-round graduates."
